      "outputs": [
        {
          "name": "stdout",
          "output_type": "stream",
          "text": [
            "Dataset size after cleaning: 10000\n",
            "\n",
            "--- Sample Before/After ---\n",
            "\n",
            "Original : This book was the very first bookmobile book I bought when I was in the school book club. I loved the story then and I b\n",
            "Cleaned  : book first bookmobile book bought school book club loved story bet dollar donut love memory serf bought book grade would\n",
            "\n",
            "Original : When I read the description for this book, I couldn't wait to read it. Once I downloaded it to my Kindle, I found it ext\n",
            "Cleaned  : read description book could wait read downloaded kindle found extremely hard keep reading honest stopped reading halfway\n",
            "\n",
            "Original : I just had to edit this review. This book is an (I believe I got this right) an updated re-write. Thank god I didn't get\n",
