          "output_type": "stream",
          "text": [
            "Loading Google News Word2Vec vectors (this may take a few minutes)...\n",
            "[==================================================] 100.0% 1662.8/1662.8MB downloaded\n",
            "✅ Loaded. Vocabulary size: 3000000\n",
            "Embedding matrix shape : (20000, 300)\n",
